Junior Corporate Lawyer NQ – 6mths PQE, Abu Dhabi
Location:  --Abu Dhabi
This highly regarded international law firm are urgently looking to recruit a junior associate to work in the firms Abu Dhabi office. The office is increasingly busy, winning a great amount of new instructions. It is a regional corporate team and the associates work on deals right across the MENA offices. The ideal candidate will be NQ-6month PQE lawyer (Sept 2013 or March 2014 qualifier) who has ideally completed 2 corporate seats. You will also have a top academic history, ideally Top 20 law firm background and already worked on international deals. Arabic language skills are preferred along with a regional training contract or a seat completed in Dubai or Abu Dhabi.
